  "original_title": "\u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd : \u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u00a0 '\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b85\u0baa\u0bcd' \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd - \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attack on President Ranil's house: If there are videos, please 'WhatsApp' - appeal to the general public",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Colombo - The police have requested that if there is footage recorded through telephones and video recording equipment, in connection with the incident of setting fire to the house of President Ranil Wickramasinghe located at No. 119 and causing damage to his car and other properties, please send them through WhatsApp.",
        "While four persons have been arrested so far in connection with this incident which took place on the 9th, a team under an Assistant Superintendent of Police of CIT has carried out investigations.",
        "In this situation, the CIDs who have made a special request through the police headquarters, have requested the general public to send such videos to their WhatsApp number 071 8594950."
      ],
